messages.message: I'm working with Resistant AI to set up a session where we can showcase our latest tech and they can showcase theirs. Before I do that, I wondered if someone could give me an update on the progress of the integration and likely timings please? Thanks!
@anna can you DM me what exactly you would need? I'm happy to help here
Thanks @david.lee - In terms of the showcase or the integration update?
Do you need someone to join for the session too? Or would a brief summary of where we are in the integration be sufficient from me?

My thinking is that if we are close to the integration, I would hold on planning the showcase session so we could combine the 2 things into a showcase of each others tech as well as showcase of the integration. If we are a way away from the integration being ready, I would proceed with the showcase just to show each other our updates to our tech for now.
I do also need some volunteers to help run the session where we show the IB side - i was thinking someone from SE team and someone from PM team to help.
Happy to lead the session Anna as I have been intro’d to their team already. I’ll reply on the integration progress part in the next few hours
I'd love to be on this session to represent product and see how we may best integrate with them
I'm also working on a RAI demo in AI Hub atm -- would love to get an invite, too :slightly_smiling_face:
@anna what's the genesis of this request? Seems like we should pull a few of these threads together
